    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Looks like this was introduced recently on the upstream wireguard-go and pulled into our fork: https://github.com/coder/wireguard-go/commit/b7cd547315bed421a648d0a0f1ee5a0fc1b1151e\r\n\r\nHowever, it has _not_ yet made it to tailscale's fork, so opening a bug against tailscale seems like poor form.",
