    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Here's the original issue I opened against Tailscale a few months ago: https://github.com/tailscale/tailscale/issues/8059\r\n\r\nThe commit I pulled in was originally meant to address this issue, but I don't think it fully solves it. My last attempt at upgrading Tailscale around then was fully stopped by this issue as CI was failing ~90% of the time with this issue, but I was only able to get the deadlock a handful of times this time.",
